      /**
 * An example to read in data
 *
 * This just copies the sysuse auto and sysuse autocmd files to files on the 
 * file system.
 *
 * @author Markus Schaffner
 */
 
// switch to the working directory
cd "~/Dropbox/Stata_conference_2015/example"

log using "log/read_data.smcl", smcl replace

// load and save the first dataset
sysuse auto, clear

save "dta/auto.dta", replace


// load and save the second dataset
sysuse autornd, clear

save "dta/autornd.dta", replace

log close

//eof
